		<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content mw-content-ltr" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Kurdish rebellion following the abolition of the Caliphate</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r963460841">@media all and (min-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .desktop-float-right{box-sizing:border-box;float:right;clear:right}}.mw-parser-output .infobox.vevent .status>p:first-child{margin:0}</style><table class="infobox vevent" style="width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;"><tbody><tr><th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Sheikh Said Rebellion</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;">Part of <a href="/wiki/Kurdish_rebellions_in_Turkey" class="mw-redirect" title="Kurdish rebellions in Turkey">Kurdish rebellions in Turkey</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;line-height:1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Cumhuriyet_March_30,_1925.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Cumhuriyet March 30, 1925.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Cumhuriyet_March_30%2C_1925.jpg/220px-Cumhuriyet_March_30%2C_1925.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="150" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Cumhuriyet_March_30%2C_1925.jpg/330px-Cumhuriyet_March_30%2C_1925.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Cumhuriyet_March_30%2C_1925.jpg/440px-Cumhuriyet_March_30%2C_1925.jpg 2x" data-file-width="774" data-file-height="527" /></a><br />Turkish soldiers encircling <a href="/wiki/Palu,_Elaz%C4%B1%C4%9F" title="Palu, Elazığ">Palu</a>, <a href="/wiki/%C3%87apaq%C3%A7ur" class="mw-redirect" title="Çapaqçur">Çapakçur</a> (present-day: Bingöl), <a href="/wiki/Solhan" title="Solhan">Genc</a> (present-day: Kaleköy, Solhan), <a href="/wiki/Dicle" title="Dicle">Piran</a>, <a href="/wiki/Hani,_Turkey" title="Hani, Turkey">Hani</a>, <a href="/wiki/Lice,_Turkey" title="Lice, Turkey">Lice</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ergani" title="Ergani">Ergani</a>, <a href="/wiki/E%C4%9Fil" title="Eğil">Egil</a> and <a href="/wiki/Silvan,_Diyarbak%C4%B1r" title="Silvan, Diyarbakır">Silvan</a>, Cumhuriyet Newspaper, 30 March 1925.</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2"><table style="width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0;display:inline-table"><tbody><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Date</th><td>8 February—March 1925<sup id="cite_ref-FOOTNOTEOlson1989107_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEOlson1989107-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Location</th><td><div class="location"><a href="/wiki/Elaz%C4%B1%C4%9F" class="mw-redirect" title="Elazığ">Elazığ</a>, <a href="/wiki/Bing%C3%B6l" title="Bingöl">Bingöl</a>, <a href="/wiki/Diyarbak%C4%B1r" title="Diyarbakır">Diyarbakır</a>, <a href="/wiki/Sanliurfa" class="mw-redirect" title="Sanliurfa">Sanliurfa</a>, <a href="/wiki/Mardin" title="Mardin">Mardin</a>, <a href="/wiki/Mu%C5%9F" title="Muş">Muş</a> areas</div></td></tr><tr><th style="padding-right:1em">Result</th><td class="status">
<p>Turkish victory
</p>
<ul><li>Revolt suppressed</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">Belligerents</th></tr><tr><td style="width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;">
