<li id="cite_note-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1067248974"/><cite id="CITEREFZülküf2015" class="citation journal cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source">Zülküf, Ergün (2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://acikerisim.artuklu.edu.tr/xmlui/bitstream/handle/20.500.12514/395/Gotara%20Dijkolonyal%20û%20Wêneyê%20Serdestiya%20Tirkan%20di%20Kovara%20Hawarê%20de.pdf?sequence=2&amp;isAllowed=y">"Gotara Dijkolonyal û Wêneyê Serdestiya Tirkan Di Kovara Hawarê De"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>Monograf</i> (in Kurdish). Artuklu University (3): 400–437.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Monograf&amp;rft.atitle=Gotara+Dijkolonyal+%C3%BB+W%C3%AAney%C3%AA+Serdestiya+Tirkan+Di+Kovara+Hawar%C3%AA+De&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=400-437&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.aulast=Z%C3%BClk%C3%BCf&amp;rft.aufirst=Erg%C3%BCn&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Facikerisim.artuklu.edu.tr%2Fxmlui%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F20.500.12514%2F395%2FGotara%2520Dijkolonyal%2520%C3%BB%2520W%C3%AAney%C3%AA%2520Serdestiya%2520Tirkan%2520di%2520Kovara%2520Hawar%C3%AA%2520de.pdf%3Fsequence%3D2%26isAllowed%3Dy&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASheikh+Said+rebellion" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
