<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1067248974"/><cite id="CITEREFOlson1989" class="citation book cs1">Olson, Robert W. (1989). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=P6lpAAAAMAAJ"><i>The emergence of Kurdish nationalism and the Sheikh Said Rebellion, 1880-1925</i></a>. University of Texas Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-292-77619-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-292-77619-7"><bdi>978-0-292-77619-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+emergence+of+Kurdish+nationalism+and+the+Sheikh+Said+Rebellion%2C+1880-1925&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Texas+Press&amp;rft.date=1989&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-292-77619-7&amp;rft.aulast=Olson&amp;rft.aufirst=Robert+W.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DP6lpAAAAMAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASheikh+Said+rebellion" class="Z3988"></span></li>
